byline.original: By ALAN RAPPEPORT and ALEXANDER BURNS

lead_paragraph: Hillary Clinton gave her concession speech on Wednesday hours after an early-morning conversation in which Mrs. Clinton conceded the presidential race to Donald J. Trump.
